{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1619/comments/6549322.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:d1ad1e84f75c..c113bcbfa7e7?path=gazebo%2Frendering%2FApplyWrenchVisual.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1619/_/diff#comment-6549322"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1619, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1619.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1619"}}, "title": "Add visuals to the Apply Force/Torque dialog"}, "content": {"raw": "You could shorten 62-89 a bit by doing something like:\n\n```\nstd::vector<std::string> entityNames = {\"__FORCE_SHAFT__\", \"__FORCE_HEAD__\", \"__TORQUE_TUBE__\", \"__TORQUE_HEAD__\"};\n\nfor (std::string entityName : entityNames)\n{\n  std::string name = this->GetName() entityName;\n  if (manager->hasEntity(name));\n    manager->destroyMovableObject(manager->getEntity(name));\n}\n```\n\nand another loop for the sceneNode objects.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>You could shorten 62-89 a bit by doing something like:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">vector</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"nt\">entityNames</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"err\">&quot;__FORCE_SHAFT__&quot;,</span> <span class=\"err\">&quot;__FORCE_HEAD__&quot;,</span> <span class=\"err\">&quot;__TORQUE_TUBE__&quot;,</span> <span class=\"err\">&quot;__TORQUE_HEAD__&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"o\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"nt\">for</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span> <span class=\"nt\">entityName</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"nt\">entityNames</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">string</span> <span class=\"n\">name</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">this-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nf\">GetName</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"n\">entityName</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"err\">if</span> <span class=\"err\">(manager-&gt;hasEntity(name))</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"err\">manager-&gt;destroyMovableObject(manager-&gt;getEntity(name))</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>and another loop for the sceneNode objects.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-04-29T00:06:47.645714+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Jackie K", "uuid": "{e3d60b62-b7c7-4863-b9b9-cdae9f123cec}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Be3d60b62-b7c7-4863-b9b9-cdae9f123cec%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Be3d60b62-b7c7-4863-b9b9-cdae9f123cec%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea011fa2919d4bd4568b32b440eda779d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsJK-0.png"}}, "nickname": "jacquelinekay", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f56c822f-f75c-4665-80f9-6e7764893b9c"}, "inline": {"to": 62, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "gazebo/rendering/ApplyWrenchVisual.cc"}, "updated_on": "2015-04-29T00:07:01.823379+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 6549322}